cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: collAIder
abstract: >
  A machine learning-based tool for predicting outcomes of stellar encounters
  using neural networks trained on Smoothed Particle Hydrodynamics (SPH)
  simulation data. collAIder classifies encounters into physical regimes
  (collision, tidal capture, flyby) and predicts post-encounter stellar masses.
